To handle the SH1106 and the SSD1305 controllers, this project includes
modified code from the provided demo code by waveshare.com. At the time the
code was imported, the provided code was not under a license.

-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+

